    <h2>In the Moment</h2>
    <p>Over at Dillyeo, we got tired of paying cruddy deal aggregator sites lots of money to drive our site traffic so we built our own. We noticed that there wasn't much happening in the space IP wise and came up with our own concept. <br><br>The boys over at Dillyeo claim to have some big plans for the re-launch of buckfiddy.com.<br><br>Buckfiddy.com was a brainchild, design and development of mine while head of Dillyeo.</p>
